        ._hover_show.__absolute
          ._trigger.p| The #[code absolute] type,
          ._item: ._content._color_1: .q| #[+repeat(4)| way too long ] 
        .s| would overlay above others.
        ._hover_show
          ._trigger.p| The #[code default] type,
          ._item: ._content._color_1: .q| #[+repeat(4)| way too long ]
        .s| would shove other content.

      style.
        #o3 ._p { white-space: nowrap }
